Its a aim-map to training the skill. This is a storage space in a bleak winter landscape. There spawnpoints for 10 Ts and 10 CTs.
For each T is a deagle, a glock and a ak_47 and for each CT a deagle, a usp and a m4 available.

Oh yes, this map is called flash, because a thunderstorm is rising:)
